Text:
@CityofSV will use the funding to widen and repair roads along Interstate 90.

And the Town of Malden is going to fund a new sewer system to get back up and running.

I am really glad to see this funding go towards projects that will make a difference for our communities.

For moms who’ve just given birth,
for families welcoming a new child,
for parents whose child is seriously ill or has a disability,
or for any worker who's been seriously ill themselves and needs time to get well,

we know that #CareCantWait. Let’s pass the #BuildBackBetter Act.
